@nike is offering a first look at the cast of characters coming together to celebrate Nike Football this summer. Featuring football stars like Cristiano Ronaldo and Erling Haaland, artists including Young Miko, and Kim Kardashian as the ultimate soccer mom, the campaign will introduce unexpected collaborations and cultural crossovers in the weeks ahead.⁠
⁠
Each figure has an authentic connection to the game, teased through exclusive Polaroid portraits shared for the first time — setting the tone for a summer where football culture extends far beyond the pitch.

